metadata.description: This connector discovers the enclosure and the disks of EMC SAN disk arrays, as well as the storage pools and storage volumes. It will also discover and monitor the FC ports of the array and the various environment sensors when available (temperatures, fans, power supplies, etc.). It relies on the WBEM technology and supports SMI-S compliant disk arrays only.

details.consequence: The network traffic handled by this adapter may be slowed down and this may affect other systems communicating with this computer.
details.recommendedAction: If possible, try to fix the problem through the network driver settings. Otherwise, replace the network adapter.
